data.description: Price Reduction! Motivated Seller.  Don't miss this one.  Newer home, only 6 years old. Less than a block away from the Hillsborough river, you can see it once you step outside your front door.  Grab your fishing gear and head out...Location is everything! This house is near the Tampa Bay Stadium, only 15 to 20 minutes from the airport very centrally located. Built in 2018, 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, beautifully open concept, large modern kitchen. with a large island where friends can gather for a meal.  The house has lots of natural light and tile through out.  The 2 car garage was converted into a large nursery /play area which includes a half bathroom with lots of potential for an in law suite with it's own private entrance.  Check out the covered lanai equipped with a fully functional kitchen.  Don't miss this one it truly is a rare gem.  It is the buyer's and/or buyer's agent responsibility to verify room measurements.
